analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) will include all patients who are randomized to study treatment. Patients will be analyzed according to the treatment arm to which they were randomized.
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) will include all patients who are randomized to study treatment. Patients will be analyzed according to the treatment arm to which they were randomized.

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The safety analysis set will include all patients who receive at least one dose of study treatment. Patients will be analyzed according to the treatment they actually received.
analysisPopulations.label: SAF
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The safety analysis set will include all patients who receive at least one dose of study treatment. Patients will be analyzed according to the treatment they actually received.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received at least one dose of study treatment

analysisPopulations.name: Per-protocol analysis set
analysisPopulations.text: The per-protocol (PP) analysis set is a subset of the FAS and will include all randomized patients who did not have any major protocol deviations that would impact the primary efficacy endpoints.
analysisPopulations.label: PP
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The per-protocol (PP) analysis set is a subset of the FAS and will include all randomized patients who did not have any major protocol deviations that would impact the primary efficacy endpoints.
analysisPopulations.criteria: FAS subset AND no major protocol deviations

analysisPopulations.name: PK analysis sets
analysisPopulations.text: The PK analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and receive at least one dose of avelumab or axitinib and have at least one measurable concentration of avelumab or axitinib.
analysisPopulations.label: PKAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The PK analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and receive at least one dose of avelumab or axitinib and have at least one measurable concentration of avelumab or axitinib.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose AND >=1 measurable concentration

analysisPopulations.name: Biomarker analysis set
analysisPopulations.text: The biomarker analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and have at least one baseline biomarker assessment.
analysisPopulations.label: BAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The biomarker analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and have at least one baseline biomarker assessment.

analysisPopulations.name: Immunogenicity analysis set
analysisPopulations.text: The immunogenicity analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and receive at least one dose of avelumab and have at least one valid ADA (anti-drug antibody) assessment.
analysisPopulations.label: IAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The immunogenicity analysis set will include all patients who are randomized and receive at least one dose of avelumab and have at least one valid ADA (anti-drug antibody) assessment.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose avelumab AND >=1 valid ADA assessment

analysisPopulations.name: PRO analysis set
analysisPopulations.text: The PRO analysis set will include all patients who are randomized, receive at least one dose of study treatment, and have at least one PRO (patient-reported outcome) assessment.
analysisPopulations.label: PROAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The PRO analysis set will include all patients who are randomized, receive at least one dose of study treatment, and have at least one PRO (patient-reported outcome) assessment.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose AND >=1 PRO assessment

characteristics.name: ECOG PS
characteristics.description: Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group Performance Status (0 vs 1)

characteristics.name: Region
characteristics.description: Geographic location (United States vs Canada/Western Europe vs Rest of World)
